---
// ImageShowcase.astro — Enhanced (Clean + Attractive + Fixed Layout)
---

<section id="image-showcase" class="content-section">
  <div class="section-container">

    <!-- Title -->
    <h2 class="section-heading">Failure Case: Stale Perception Under Challenging Conditions</h2>

    <!-- Highlighted Intro Box -->
    <div class="problem-intro-box">

      <p class="section-intro">
        Under real-world vibration, <strong>low-value, redundant and distorted sensor streams</strong> delay critical observations. 
        As a result, perception operates on <strong>stale inputs</strong>,leading to missed detections and unsafe decisions.
      </p>

      <p class="group-description">
        The left shows failure under vibration-induced stale perception, while the right highlights improved sensing with adaptive filtering.
      </p>

    </div>

    <!-- Comparison -->
    <div class="image-pair">

      <!-- BEFORE -->
      <div class="image-card">
        <span class="tag tag-bad">Stale Perception</span>

        <iframe 
          src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1R2sQOs8LKBlH2kDEpd74cFOKFQpBsW0X/preview"
          allow="autoplay"
          title="Failure video">
        </iframe>
      </div>

      <!-- AFTER -->
      <div class="image-card">
        <span class="tag tag-good">Adaptive Sensing</span>

        <img 
          src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1RfFGE0oFWyu_Y5CMWwD_ZAvSUXCY-Ycw&sz=w1000"
          alt="Improved sensing"
        />
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>

/* ===== SECTION ===== */
.content-section {
  padding: 4rem 2rem 3rem;
}

.section-container {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: auto;
}

/* ===== HEADING ===== */
.section-heading {
  font-size: 1.65rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #223253;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  position: relative;
}

.section-heading::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -6px;
  left: 0;
  width: 55px;
  height: 3px;
  background: #c05e3c;
}

/* ===== INTRO BOX ===== */
.problem-intro-box {
  padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem;
  border-radius: 12px;

  background: linear-gradient(
    135deg,
    rgba(192,94,60,0.06),
    rgba(34,50,83,0.03)
  );

  border: 1px solid rgba(192,94,60,0.1);

  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  transition: all 0.25s ease;
}

.problem-intro-box:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

/* ===== MAIN TEXT (FIXED WIDTH ISSUE) ===== */
.section-intro {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 100%;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.85;
  color: #444;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;

  text-align: justify;
  text-justify: inter-word;
}

.section-intro strong {
  color: #c05e3c;
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* ===== DESCRIPTION ===== */
.group-description {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: #666;

  text-align: justify;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

/* ===== IMAGE PAIR ===== */
.image-pair {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.4rem;
}

/* ===== CARD ===== */
.image-card {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 14px;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: #111;

  aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;

  border: 1px solid #e4e8ef;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.image-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-6px);
  box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}

/* ===== MEDIA ===== */
.image-card iframe,
.image-card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border: none;
  transition: transform 0.4s ease;
}

.image-card:hover img,
.image-card:hover iframe {
  transform: scale(1.04);
}

/* ===== TAGS ===== */
.tag {
  position: absolute;
  top: 12px;
  left: 12px;
  padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  border-radius: 20px;
  color: white;
  z-index: 2;
}

.tag-bad {
  background: rgba(200, 60, 60, 0.9);
}

.tag-good {
  background: rgba(40, 140, 90, 0.9);
}

/* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .image-pair {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .section-intro,
  .group-description {
    text-align: left;
  }
}

</style>